      <title>特朗普捍卫经济议程，称关税将促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/trump-defends-economic-agenda-saying-tariffs-will-fuel-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，尽管他的政策会增加债务，但他的政策将促进增长，他试图安抚那些担心他的经济计划会加剧通胀的商界领袖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/trump-defends-economic-agenda-saying-tariffs-will-fuel-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长筹款活动因市政厅人员外流和调查增多而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/nyc-mayor-s-fundraising-slows-as-city-hall-exodus-probes-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 自 7 月中旬以来已为其 2025 年连任竞选筹集了 19 万美元，这是他担任市长以来收到的最低捐款额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/nyc-mayor-s-fundraising-slows-as-city-hall-exodus-probes-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:31:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙极右翼政党 Chega 将投票反对预算计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/portugal-s-far-right-chega-party-to-vote-against-budget-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙极右翼“切加”党是议会第三大政治力量，该党计划投票反对该国少数派政府提出的 2025 年预算计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/portugal-s-far-right-chega-party-to-vote-against-budget-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:13:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>若特朗普宣布加征关税，欧盟将制定针对美国的贸易目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/eu-readies-us-trade-targets-if-election-brings-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果前总统唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选并履行其对欧盟采取惩罚性贸易措施的威胁，欧盟将列出可能加征关税的美国商品清单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/eu-readies-us-trade-targets-if-election-brings-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺沃亚称，犯罪团伙正在厄瓜多尔种植可卡因的主要原料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/gangs-now-growing-key-cocaine-ingredient-in-ecuador-noboa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚表示，贩毒团伙已开始在厄瓜多尔境内大量种植古柯，古柯是制造可卡因的主要原料。诺沃亚誓言要根除古柯作物，作为持续打击困扰该国的贩毒活动的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/gangs-now-growing-key-cocaine-ingredient-in-ecuador-noboa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:03:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国称马杜罗使用“镇压机器”对付对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/maduro-wielded-machinery-of-repression-against-rivals-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国一个小组称，委内瑞拉七月有争议的选举后，“大规模参与”了构成反人类罪的侵犯人权行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/maduro-wielded-machinery-of-repression-against-rivals-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼将召集欧盟志同道合的同行，寻求更严格的移民规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/meloni-to-gather-eu-like-minded-counterparts-seeking-tougher-migration-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼将在本周的欧盟峰会期间召集领导人举行非正式会议，以推动采取更严格的移民措施，因为欧盟内部在这一问题上的分歧正在扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/meloni-to-gather-eu-like-minded-counterparts-seeking-tougher-migration-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言将自行决定如何攻击伊朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/israel-vows-it-will-make-its-own-decision-on-how-to-attack-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，以色列政府正在听取美国的恳求，将核能和能源设施从其目标名单中剔除，以限制升级风险。此后，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡坚称，以色列可以自由选择对伊朗采取反击行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/israel-vows-it-will-make-its-own-decision-on-how-to-attack-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:39:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国担心中国黑客入侵关键基础设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-fears-chinese-hackers-compromised-critical-infrastructure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国官员称，中国政府行为者已大范围、并可能成功侵入英国关键基础设施网络，这凸显出英国对日益复杂的外国网络攻击的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-fears-chinese-hackers-compromised-critical-infrastructure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:25:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
